# Node version

`package.json` sets **`engines.node": ">=22.12.0"`** (Astro 6 requirement).

- Local **`npm run build`** / **`astro`** may fail on older Node (e.g. 20.x) with an engine error.
- Use **Node 22.12+** locally, or run commands in a **Node 22** container (see `docker-bind-mount-node` rule).

Do not lower the engine range to silence errors without confirming Astro compatibility.
